            </li>
        </ol>
    </li>
</ol>

<ol start = '4'>
    <li class = 'bigQuestion'>
        A person lifts a box with a weight of 200 Newtons.
        The person is lifting the box upward, but it is <emph>slowing down</emph> as it rises.
        The only forces to consider on the box are the contact force caused by the person's arms
